---
title: Crunchy Pork Burgers with Secret Sauce and Sweet Potato Wedges
description: This crunchy pork burger is putting the 'ham' back in hamburger! Pair it with our creamy secret sauce and some spiced sweet potato wedges, and burger night may never be the same!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/burgers-de-porc-croustillant-3e918452.jpg
